# AI-Powered Fabric Sourcing Assistant

## Overview
This project is a voice-enabled web application that converts speech into structured fabric order details.

## Features
- Voice-to-text using Web Speech API
- Auto form filling using Python Flask backend
- Editable form fields
- Summary page

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: HTML, JavaScript
- Backend: Flask (Python)

## How to Run
1. Install dependencies:
   pip install flask

2. Run:
   python app.py

3. Open:
   http://127.0.0.1:5000